import re

def parse_svg_data(svg_code: str) -> dict:
    total_users_match = re.search('', svg_code)
    total_earnings_match = re.search('<text.*?>(\\$[\\d,]+\\.\\d+)</text>', svg_code)
    total_users = int(total_users_match.group(1))
    total_earnings = float(total_earnings_match.group(1).replace('$', '').replace(',', ''))
    return {'total_users': total_users, 'total_earnings': total_earnings}
